dc_title_s: Republic of Georgia administrative GIS spatial data [FSU-AC3+]
dc_description_s: ACASIAN. Title supplied by cataloger. Copyright Griffith University. Includes ADM1 and ADM2 administrative units and capitals for the Republic of Georgia, current to the early to mid 2000s.  The spatial data are geo-referenced in decimal degrees using the WSG84 Spheriod, and incorporate DCW coastlines and international boundaries. System requirements: IBM or compatible computer; CD-ROM drive; software capable of reading an ESRI shapefile, such as ArcGIS.
dc_publisher_s: Australian Centre of the Asian Spatial Information and Analysis Network
dc_creator_sm: Asian Spatial Information and Analysis Network (Australia) Australian Centre
